   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Frame agreement with NGO (Fida Int.)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Gender Mainstreaming and Advocacy Project. The purpose of the project is to improve gender mainstreaming and competence within projects and local partner organizations. Fida is working with national churches in Ethiopia_ Kenya_ Tanzania_ Uganda and Sudan. The partners&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99; competence is raised and gender mainstreaming advocated through awareness-raising and training of trainers. Also monitoring already existing projects in terms of gender is part of the process. The partners are involved at all levels: from the preparation of materials to planning and implementation at the local level. As the competence and understanding among the partners on gender related questions builds up_ they will be increasingly able to apply their learning in practice. Gender becomes an integral part of all project planning_ implementation and monitoring. This will lead towards the increase of gender equality in the local communities in which the churches work.</narrative>
  </description>
